      "name": "Achiever's Section",
      "description": "Contains Higher Order Thinking Questions of the same topics as in Section 2."
    }
  ],
  "exam_pattern_notes": [
    "In NSO Level-1 exam, 60% of the questions will be from the current class syllabus and 40% from the previous class syllabus.",
